                                                                              ðŸ”¢ NUMPY âˆ’ NDARRAY OBJECT
--> ðŸŽ€ What is ndarray?
     NumPy ka core data structure hai â€” ndarray (N-dimensional array).
     Yeh ek fast, homogenous (same datatype) array hota hai.

--> Syntax
    import numpy as np
    arr = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4, 5])
    print(arr)
    print(type(arr))

--> ðŸ”¹ Array Attributes
         | Attribute  |     Description      |    Example     |
         | ---------- | -------------------- | -------------- |
         | `ndim`     | Number of dimensions | `arr.ndim`     |
         | `shape`    | Rows Ã— Columns       | `arr.shape`    |
         | `size`     | Total elements       | `arr.size`     |
         | `dtype`    | Data type            | `arr.dtype`    |
         | `itemsize` | Bytes per element    | `arr.itemsize` |
